You can make an anonymous checkout via git:

Use the git protocol for optimum efficiency and download speed:
git clone git://git.mercenariesguild.net/plutocracy.git

Use http if you you're behind a proxy and that's all you have:
git clone http://git.mercenariesguild.net/plutocracy.git

Also, you can see the git repository webpage:
firefox http://git.mercenariesguild.net/
